			XPCE Document rendering library
			-------------------------------


Created:	Tue Feb  8 2000
History:
----------------------------------------------------------------

Description
-----------

This library provides a high-level interface   to the document rendering
primitives of XPCE. Please consult  the   XPCE  UserGuide for a detailed
overview of the primitives as well as this library.


Primitives defined
------------------

XPCE Primitive	File       	Description
-------------------------------------------------------------------
<objects>	objects.pl	Reusable objects used for rendering
vfont		vfont.pl	Virtual (logical) font
doc_mode	layout.pl	Rendering mode parameters
pbox		layout.pl	Parbox with event-handling
button_box	layout.pl	Mark begin/end active area
anchor_box	layout.pl	Mark begin/end link-target
bullet_list	layout.pl	Unordered list environment
enum_list	layout.pl	Ordered list environment
definition_list	layout.pl	Definition list environment
doc_table	table.pl	Table rendering
doc_window	window.pl	Window holding a pbox
doc_browser	browser.pl	Simple WWW browser

Predicates	File       	Description
-------------------------------------------------------------------
html_tokens/2	html/2		Translate HTML file into Prolog term
